<subSubSection pageId="11" pageNumber="404" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="11.[2039,2633,2070,2497]" pageId="11" pageNumber="404">
Widely used subspecies name colchica changed for gender agreement. Evidence from mtDNA and nDNA sequences classifies S. volnuchiniin the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1766" box="[2362,2468,2306,2339]" class="Mammalia" family="Soricidae" genus="Sorex" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="11" pageNumber="404" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="minutus">minutus</taxonomicName>
group. Two subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
